*Galax urceolata* (Poir.) Brummitt

BELL CO.: ca. 1.5 mi SW of Pineville. Pine
Mountain State Nature Preserve, near lodge, along
Hemlock Garden Trail.

Mesic forest dominated by *Tsuga canadensis*, *Nyssa
sylvatica*, *Quercus* spp., and *Magnolia
macrophylla*; infrequent.
